rule_prop_value: select BANKID from Bank where BANKCODE not in ('BARC','HSBC')
select BANKID from Bank where length(POSTALCODE) <> 5
select Transaction_Identifier  from  Payments where Payment_Method ='Cheque' and length(cast (Cheque_Number as STRING))<6
select Transaction_Identifier  from  Payments where Payment_Method <> 'Cheque' and (Cheque_Number IS not NULL or trim(cast (Cheque_Number as STRING))<> '')
select Transaction_Identifier  from  Payments where Transaction_Date > Current_Date()
